<!DOCTYPE html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>button-1</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/button-1.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./../css/reset.css">

    <body>
        <h1 class="center">没有图标:定宽定高文字居中(一样大小),可扩展,统一背景(单div)</h1>
        <div class="button shadow">
            <span class="icon">圆角按钮</span>
        </div>
        <a class="button">
            <span class="icon">纯色按钮</span>
        </a>
        <h1 class="center">只有图标,没有文字</h1>
        <a class="button">
           <span class="icon">
				<span class="img"></span>
        	</span>
        </a>
        <div class="button shadow">
        	<span class="icon">
				<span class="img"></span>
        	</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="center">没有图标:左右间距固定,文字自动撑开,可扩展背景</h1>
        <div class="center">
        	<div class="button2">
        		<span class="icon">Luobata</span>
        	</div>
        </div>
        <div class="center">
        	<div class="button2 shadow">
        		<span class="icon">Luobata</span>
        	</div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="center">有图标,图标在x:x边定宽,右边文字撑开</h1>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 left">
            	<span class="icon">
            		<span class="img"></span>
                	<span class="txt">点赞~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span>
            	</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 right shadow">
            	<span class="icon">
            		<span class="img"></span>
                	<span class="txt">点赞</span>
            	</span>
            </div>
        </div>        
        <h1 class="center">图标在X,带竖杠</h1>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 left">
            	<span class="icon">
	                <span class="img"></span>
	                <span class="shugang"></span>
	                <span class="txt">sdasdasdsadsasda</span>            		
            	</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 right shadow">
            	<span class="icon">
	                <span class="img"></span>
	                <span class="shugang right"></span>
	                <span class="txt">349128943</span>
            	</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 shadow">
            	<span class="icon">
	                <span class="img icon_left"></span>
	                <span class="shugang"></span>
	                <span class="txt txt_center">点一下试试</span>
	                <span class="shugang right"></span>
	                <span class="img icon_right"></span>
            	</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</head>

</html>
